snippet.title: "inhe ghuske maro", says Akshay Kumar over Pathankot attack

localized.description:
Actor Akshay Kumar on Monday expressed anguish at Pathankot attack in which 7 Indian soldiers attained martyrdom. Akshay said he has no power to find a final solution to terrorism. “I don’t have a final solution to the problem. But the way they entered our country and murdered our soldiers, I will say ‘inhe ghuske maro’,” he said.
